title: Miron Muslic
text:
Miron Muslic (born 14 September 1982) is an Austrian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> coach and a former player who played as a <a href="forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a>.
Coaching career.
On 14 July 2020, he was hired as a manager by <a href="Austrian%20Football%20Second%20League">Austrian Football Second League</a> club <a href="Floridsdorfer%20AC">Floridsdorfer AC</a>.
